replies.msg:
Coutinho: &quot;In the last few weeks, months even, I've not been playing well. But I still want to improve. I came to Barcelona to give my best. I live for the moment. You never know what the future holds. I am happy with my performance today.&quot;<br />
<br />
Piqu&eacute;: &quot;When I see Luis is tired, I ask the coach to put me up front, but he does not do it... Let's see if I can achieve it by scoring more goals... Leo has played a great game, two goals and two assists.&quot;

